0/netflix-wants-a-grand-theft-auto-game-on-its-service-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/netflix-wants-a-grand-theft-auto-game-on-its-service-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/netflix-wants-a-grand-theft-auto-game-on-its-service-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3516429" class="wp-caption-text"> 《侠盗猎车手 5》来源：Take-Two Interactive</figcaption></figure><p> <em>《华尔街日报》</em>的消息人士继续透露，还有意开发和推出受<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/black-mirror">《黑镜》</a> 、《惊天营救》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/squid-game">《鱿鱼游戏》</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-interviews/wednesday-interview-jenna-ortega-behind-the-scenes-3346075"><em>《星期三》</em></a>启发的游戏。</p><p>为了进军游戏领域，Netflix 在过去几年收购了 Boss Fight Entertainment、Next Games、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/night-school-studio">Night School Studio</a>和 Spry Fox 等工作室。与此同时，两家新游戏工作室将于 2022 年在加利福尼亚和芬兰开业。</p><p>此外，据信 Netflix 迄今已在其游戏策略上花费了约 8.22 亿英镑（10 亿美元）。</p><p>然而，游戏并不是 Netflix 独占的利基市场。 <em>《华尔街日报》</em>提到，Netflix 并不从其游戏中产生收入，订阅者可以在其特定计划之外免费访问这些游戏。 </p><figure id="attachment_3516430" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3516430" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3516430" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/netflix-wants-a-grand-theft-auto-game-on-its-service-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/netflix-wants-a-grand-theft-auto-game-on-its-service-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/netflix-wants-a-grand-theft-auto-game-on-its-service-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/netflix-wants-a-grand-theft-auto-game-on-its-service-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/netflix-wants-a-grand-theft-auto-game-on-its-service-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-conten